{"tid":1934587,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港快運下周一起至下月底暫停營運所有航班","createTime":"2020-03-20T04:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T04:42:58.000Z","uid":236171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eebee3da36ed3ac24ed7264bbdaa72e885c0b998","tid":1934587,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515733-20200320.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515733-20200320.htm&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBKwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=b7882063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515733-20200320.htm&h=9e7e6b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515733-20200320.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港快運HK Express宣布，將暫時停止本月23至下月30日期間的所有航班營運。<br />\n<br />\n香港快運表示，新型冠狀病毒於全球大流行的情況持續，導致香港政府及亞洲多國相繼頒佈多項入境限制，以及旅遊需求大幅下降。<br />\n<br />\n公司將密切留意疫情發展，計劃於5月1日恢復航班營運，官網會繼續出售今年5月起出發的機票。凡因航線暫停營運而受影響的旅客，可獲提供更改出發日期、更改航線或全數退款的安排選擇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港快運表示，會將機組人員原先分配於今年較後時間放的年假，提前於4至6月期間放，確保恢復航班營運時，有足夠前線人手應付需求。公司亦已採取多項措施，包括凍結職位招聘、推行「特別無薪假計劃」等，以減輕疫情對企業財政造成的影響。"},{"pid":"70398f53aec718b0aef1e716791707e31c559e09","tid":1934587,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"無得去旅行lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baab6a7e3fec4cb1ad7338979f4002fc5a0f6ec","tid":1934587,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}